This directory now owns the HTML/book workflow around alignment:

- `parse_index.py`: parse a LibriVox index page into a YAML book config
- `fetch_text.py`: fetch and clean reference text
- `align.py`: book-level wrapper that calls the shared alignment engine in `align_whisper/`

The actual ASR/text alignment logic lives in `align_whisper/`. `align.py` keeps
the old `align-html` CLI (`--whisperx`, `--text`, `--config`) but no longer has
its own separate alignment implementation.
